    Btrfs: Fix incorrect inode nlink in btrfs_link()
    
    Link count of the inode is not decreased if btrfs_set_inode_index()
    fails.
    
    Signed-off-by: Miao Xie <miaox@cn.fujitsu.com>
    Singed-off-by: Li Zefan <lizf@cn.fujitsu.com>

